%h4 It's completely anonymous and fun.

.btn{ 'ng-click' => 'loadSampleDialectics()' } Browse sample classes

.nothing{ 'ng-hide' => 'samples' }
  %br
  %h3 Learn more about Moving Teachings by watching this short video.
  %h4 Take and teach mini classes on the bus.
